						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in the Mahāliṅgēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 14th century.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record refers to gift of land for feeding Brāhmaṇas. It mentions Maṇavūr. All details are lost.</p>						

